walkthrough.initialSetup.title: Start using dbt Power User
walkthrough.initialSetup.description: Start using dbt in vscode by opening a dbt project.
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.open.desc:
To start off, open a dbt project. If you are just beginning to explore dbt, try out the jaffle-shop project (link).
[Check Setting](command:vscode.openFolder)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.selectInt:
This step will change a setting and check off when the setting has changed
[Change Setting](command:python.setInterpreter)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.updateExt:
To get the latest features, update the dbt Power User extension.
[Update Extension](command:workbench.extensions.action.updateExtension?%22innoverio.vscode-dbt-power-user%22)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.associate:
Associate file types with dbt Power User.
[Associate File Types](command:dbtPowerUser.associateFileExts)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.validateP: Check if projects are set up correction.

Check if projects are set up correction.
[Validate Project](command:dbtPowerUser.validateProject)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.installDe:
Install packages in dbt projects. This step will run dbt deps.
[Run dbt deps](command:dbtPowerUser.installDeps)
